        <updateDate>2007-11-05T22:49:40Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>National Commission on Detainee Treatment Act of 2007 - Establishes the National Commission on Detainee Treatment to: (1) conduct a comprehensive review of matters relating to the capture, custody, judicial proceedings, and repatriation of suspected unlawful enemy combatants; and (2) prepare and submit to Congress and the President a final report on Commission recommendations, findings, and conclusions. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
